////AC joint - Degeneration

Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I'm on Page 05 - AC-Joint & Rotator Cuff of Shoulder MRI
When I select the radio button 'Finding'
Then 'Finding' dropdown menu is enabled
When I select 'AC joint' from the Finding dropdown
Then 'Add new finding' button is enabled
And 'Degeneration' radio button is enabled
And 'Trauma' radio button is enabled
And 'Inflammation' radio button is enabled

And 'Serial number' input field is enabled
And 'Image number' input field is enabled
And 'Import reference image' image uploader field is enabled

When I select 'Degeneration' radio button
Then 'Osteophytes' checkbox is enabled
And 'Capsular hypertrophy' checkbox is enabled
And 'Subchondral cysts' checkbox is enabled
And 'Subchondral edema' checkbox is enabled
And 'Articular effusion' checkbox is enabled
And 'Sclerosis' checkbox is enabled
And 'Osteolysis, lateral clavicles' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Osteolysis, lateral clavicles' checkbox
Then 'Cortical thinning' checkbox is enabled
And 'Cortical bone erosion' checkbox is enabled
